        <item>
            <title>Starlink 现金流实现收支平衡　将继续发射更多衞星扩充网络</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=starlink-breakeven-cash-flow</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 16:56:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SpaceX]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Starlink]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203046</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>SpaceX 的 Starlink 衞星网络服务一直是他们的核心业务之一，近年密锣紧鼓的扩充下，最近终于实现了现金流收支平衡，未来可望成为独立公司上市招股。<br /><span id="more-1203046"></span></p><p>SpaceX 本身在 2022 年已经录得现金流脱离赤字的轨道，而且在 2023 年也继续录得黑字，至于旗下 Starlink 衞星网络服务，最近 Elon Musk 在 X 上透露也终于实现现金流收支平衡，同时已经占有目前运作中衞星之中的最大份额，在明年内更会成为人类所发射的所有衞星之中，占最大比例的种类。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Excited to announce that <a href="https://twitter.com/SpaceX?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@SpaceX</a><a href="https://twitter.com/Starlink?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Starlink</a> has achieved breakeven cash flow! Excellent work by a great team.</p><p>Starlink is also now a majority of all active satellites and will have launched a a majority of all satellites cumulatively from Earth by next year.</p><p>&mdash; Elon Musk (@elonmusk) <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1720098480037773658?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 2, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>目前为止 Starlink 已经发射超过 5,000 个衞星，用户超过 200 万，带领 SpaceX 估值提升至超过 1,500 亿美元。Elon Musk 之前曾经透露 Starlink 有机会分拆上市募资，不过就要等到最快 2025 年之后。</p><p>来源：X</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/">Starlink 现金流实现收支平衡　将继续发射更多衞星扩充网络</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/05/starlink-breakeven-cash-flow/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Microsoft 员工 Xbox 福利被削减　不再享有免费 Xbox Game Pass Ultimate</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-removed/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-removed</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-removed/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 09:59:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[xbox]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203042</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>科技企业的员工福利向来不错，Microsoft 的员工一直以来都拥有免费获得 Xbox Game Pass Ultimate 的福利，不过在明年 1 月开始这个福利将会取消，原因未明。<br /><span id="more-1203042"></span></p><p>据报导指，Microsoft 上星期开始通知员工，所有全职 Microsoft 员工明年 1 月起将不再享有免费 Xbox Game Pass Ultimate 福利，如果想继续使用，可以在内部商店以折扣价订阅。部分员工在内部通讯平台表示不满，也要求 Xbox 负责人 Phil Spencer 回应，不过 Phil Spencer 表示他自己事前也不知道这个政策变化，正在了解情况。</p><p>Xbox Game Pass 在几个月前加价，不过 Microsoft 近年并没有向外公开订阅人数，因此加价有否影响用户增长则无法得知，而 Microsoft 方面也未有解释为什么会停止提供这个员工福利。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/2/23944124/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-removed">Verge</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-removed/fun-tech/">Microsoft 员工 Xbox 福利被削减　不再享有免费 Xbox Game Pass Ultimate</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/microsoft-xbox-game-pass-ultimate-free-employee-removed/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
