        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Google Bard 终可实时回应问题，像 Bing 一样随时中断回复</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/google-bard-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-bard-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/google-bard-2/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 Nov 2023 04:24:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Bard]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1201937</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 ChatGPT、Bing Chat 等生成式 AI 正不断改进的同时，Google Bard 最近亦推出一系列最新功能，当中包括实时回复、跳过回应等。</p><p>新加入的「实时回复」功能中，用家可像 Bing 一样在答案生成途中，就可一句一句显示答案，毋须好像以前一样要生成整个答案才可看到。如果用家不喜欢 Google Bard 全新的实时回复功能，只需在 Google Bard 视窗右上角的齿轮图示上，将「实时回复」选项转成「完成后回复」，便可关闭即时回复功能，Google Bard 将以以往的方式回复用家问题。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.04.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1201938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.04-694x343.png" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.04-694x343.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.04-1280x633.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.04-768x380.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.04-1536x760.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.04.png 1556w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外，若然用家对 Google Bard 正在生成的回复不满意，只需直接按下提示框上方的「跳过回应」便可中途切断机械人的对话，Google Bard 便会停止生成回复，使用家可直接重新输入新问题或指令。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.58.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1201939" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.58-694x140.png" alt="" width="694" height="140" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.58-694x140.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.58-1280x257.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.58-768x154.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.58-1536x309.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-30-07.43.58.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>另外，用家更可在全新的「查看其他草稿」中查看 Google Bard 的其他回复。Google 亦允许用家修改回复，使其回复方或更「随意」或 「专业」，并可点击底部菜单栏中的 Google 徽标，与搜索中的讯息反复核对任何答案。</p><p>除了上述功能外，Google Bard 还推出其他更新，包括让用家能在分享对话中看到上传的图片等。若然如果用家将 Bard 与 Gmail 一起使用，Bard 更可一次概括多个电邮，Google 称该功能可更好地让用家知道何时需查看最新电邮。</p><p>图片来源：9to5Google.</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/27/23935437/google-bard-chatbot-real-time-responses">The Verge</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/04/google-bard-2/fun-tech/">Google Bard 终可实时回应问题，像 Bing 一样随时中断回复</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
